Data Processing Engines

R6 classes are used as processing engines for reading, processing, inspecting and storing data.

Project Headers

The ProjectHeaders S7 class is used to manage and store project headers (i.e. metadata) in the processing engines.

ProjectHeaders()
ProjectHeaders S7 class constructor, slots and methods

Processing settings

A data processing workflow in StreamFind is assemble by creating an ordered list of proessing settings objects. Each processing method is assigened to a processing engine and an algorithm.
